      <title>摩根大通等多家银行正在为英国公司 Belron 处理超过 80 亿欧元的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/belron-set-to-launch-over-8-billion-in-debt-for-refinancing-and-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根大通、法国巴黎银行和美国银行等银行将向英国汽车玻璃维修和更换公司 Belron 发行超过 80 亿欧元（88 亿美元）的债券，所得款项将用于延长债务到期日和为股东分红提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/belron-set-to-launch-over-8-billion-in-debt-for-refinancing-and-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
