      <title>布鲁克菲尔德的 Hyler 认为房地产市场在经历两年低迷后将回暖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brookfield-s-hyler-sees-thaw-in-real-estate-after-two-year-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司表示，随着经济状况好转，房地产市场正在反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brookfield-s-hyler-sees-thaw-in-real-estate-after-two-year-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
